{% extends "_templates/base.njk" %}

{% set title = "Iconic Music Flyers" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="container py-5">
  <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">Iconic Music Flyers Across Eras</h1>
  <p class="lead mb-4">
  Before social media and streaming, flyers were the lifeline of live music â€” buzzing on telephone poles, record store windows, and city streets. 
  These hand-crafted designs didn't just advertise shows; they captured the spirit of entire scenes. 
  This page showcases the iconic flyers that brought fans together and left a lasting visual stamp on music culture.
</p>

  <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3 g-4">
    {% for flyer in flyers %}
    <div class="col">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <img src="/img/{{ flyer.image }}" alt="{{ flyer.title }}" class="card-img-top">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">{{ flyer.title }}</h5>
          <p class="card-text">{{ flyer.description }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
